Package: finder-linux
Version: 1.0-1
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Manish Bhoumik <manishbhoumik0@gmail.com>
Depends: xdg-utils
Recommends: nemo | nautilus | dolphin | thunar
Description: macOS-style Finder launcher for Linux
 A branded launcher that wraps existing Linux file managers
 (Nemo, Nautilus, Dolphin, Thunar) with a macOS-style "Finder"
 experience. Includes quick-access desktop actions for common
 folders and a custom icon set.
